+Each test names a production dependency and the representative mutation that
+must make it fail.  The inventory-driven cases intentionally derive their
+parameter set from ``config_inventory()`` so a newly inventoried TOML setting
+is exercised automatically rather than relying on a hand-maintained key list.
+"""
